data.title: Seychelles Population size - data, chart
data.meta_description: The Seychelles: Population size, in millions: The latest value from 2023 is 0.12 million, unchanged from 0.12 million in 2022. In comparison, the world average is 40.69 million, based on data from 196 countries. Historically, the average for the Seychelles from 1960 to 2023 is 0.07 million. The minimum value, 0.04 million, was reached in 1960 while the maximum of 0.12 million was recorded in 2022.
